  • Uses of Matrix4x3fStack in org.joml

    Methods in org.joml that return Matrix4x3fStack 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    Matrix4x3fStack Matrix4x3fStack.clear()
    Set the stack pointer to zero and set the current/bottom matrix to identity.
    Matrix4x3fStack Matrix4x3fStack.popMatrix()
    Decrement the stack pointer by one.
    Matrix4x3fStack Matrix4x3fStack.pushMatrix()
    Increment the stack pointer by one and set the values of the new current matrix to the one directly below it.
